Title: Tired of uploading your files to random tool websites? I built a 100% local, no-signup utility hub with 26 tools.

Body:
If you are like me and hate having to sign up or risk your privacy just to compress an image, extract video frames, format JSON, or compute financial loans, give playiee.com a shot.

It's a completely free, dark-themed toolkit housing 26 practical micro-apps. Because almost everything executes locally via your browser's client-side JavaScript, your files and inputs are never uploaded to any server.

No catches, no account creation, just raw utility whenever you need it. Let me know what you think!

👉 https://playiee.com
